Abstract
--------
This piece of software is my personal take on an Arduino library
for controlling the Maxim MAX7219 LED controller IC.

Further infos
-------------
You can view the documentation for the library at 
http://www.icanmakeit.de/category/make/projects/icmi-max7219-arduino-lib/

You can watch a video showing the BasicFunctionDemo sketch in action at
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RK2xP-nQUcU


